titles.title: A bill to suspend temporarily the duty on 5-Chloro-2-(2,4-dichlorophenoxy) phenol.

action.text: Referred to the Committee on Finance.

bill.summary: 3/9/1994--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend, through December 31, 1996, the duty on 5-chloro-2(2, 4 dichlorophenoxy) phenol.
